6. Conclusion and improvisation: [ Score: 5 point ]¶

Write your conclusion on the results.

Detailed suggestions or improvements or on quality, quantity, variety, velocity, veracity etc. on the data points collected by the telecom operator to perform a better data analysis in future.

Conclusion :¶

AdaBoostClassifier method with n_estimators=10 is the best trained model, as it has the highest number of true positives with a recall of 57.48%

Also, it has one of the best prediction accuracies with test data set at 79.76%

GradientBoostingClassifier method with n_estimators = 50 has a prediction accuracy of 79.95% with test data but the recall is just 50.27%

Improvisation :¶

  1. Parameters such as age and city would have helped in better prediction, as they have high importance considering telecom industry
  2. The quantity of data could have been higher (over 50,000 rows), along with the above metioned parameters
  3. Generally men use more telecom services than women. But in this dataset, both genders show similar characteristics due to which, gender as a feature had no importance. A larger and realistic data could have improved prediction accuracy.
